ue)\n      out.flush()\n      bytes.toByteArray\n    } finally {\n      out.close()\n    }\n  }\n\n  private def deserialize(bytes: Array[Byte]): AnyRef = {\n    val in: ObjectInputStream = new ObjectInputStream(new ByteArrayInputStream(bytes))\n    try {\n      in.readObject().asInstanceOf[AnyRef]\n    } finally {\n      in.close()\n    }\n  }\n}\n"}
